            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-orange-500/20 to-orange-600/20 rounded-xl p-8 border border-orange-500/50">
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4 text-orange-400">Pro</h3>
          <ul class="text-left space-y-3 text-slate-300">
            <li class="flex gap-3">
              <span class="text-orange-400">‚úì</span>
              <span>Everything in Free</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex gap-3">
              <span class="text-orange-400">‚úì</span>
              <span>Versioned cloud backups</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex gap-3">
              <span class="text-orange-400">‚úì</span>
              <span>Inventory sharing</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex gap-3">
